metadata.title: Support of camera modules with 18pin interface?

sections.content:
Question:
Support of camera modules with 18pin interface?
Answer:
Yes, camera modules with 18pin interface is supported aligned to pin 1 of J6 on the AIK-RA6M3.
Suitable Products
AIK-RA6M3
